What is the mass of the suspended weight, [`D`], if the tension in rope *AB* is [`T_{AB}=`] [`[$TensionA]`] [`\textrm{N}`] and [`\theta=`] [`[$angleBC]`] [`^{\circ}`]?

[`D=`][___]{"$Mass"} [`\textrm{kg}`] 

